[src:simplex-algorithm/interior-point-method] Then, it is updated according to the following rule: $t_{i+1}:=\mu \cdot t_{i}$ .
[src:simplex-algorithm/interior-point-method] For each *ti*, we find an approximate minimum of *fti*, denoted by *xi*.
[src:simplex-algorithm/interior-point-method] To find *xi*+1, we start with *xi* and apply the damped Newton method.
